{"tid":2096660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】新垣結衣寫真展7月中開幕","createTime":"2020-07-06T09:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T09:30:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a52dc320896c549b9f1d26a97209c92b4ddd73ab","tid":2096660,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"「國民老婆」新垣結衣去年將自己由2010年到2019年期間拍攝過的寫真集合一身從新推出合輯寫真集《YUI ARAGAKI NYLON JAPAN ARCHIVE BOOK 2010-2019》，當中還包括結衣BB為時裝雜誌《NYLON JAPAN》近十年來為結衣拍攝的封面和內頁照片，全本寫真總共324頁，收錄719張包含沒有在連載中刊登的照片，以及專門拍攝的38頁寫真，雖然售價較一般寫真貴，售8,800日圓（約$635港幣），但銷量亦沒受影響，2020年上半年共售出25,966本，在排行日本寫真排行榜第十位。<br />\n<br />\n而7月16日至27日，日本澀谷PARCO「GALLERY X」舉辦名為「YUI ARAGAKI NYLON JAPAN ARCHIVE BOOK 2010-2019 PHOTO EXHIBITION」的結衣BB寫真展，會將結衣BB寫真集中從未公開的照片一井展出，展現結衣BB休閒一面，現場更有原創限定袋及明信片等精品發售，而展覽的入場費為700日圓（約$50港幣）。而由於受到新冠肺炎疫情的影響，大會更特設網上寫真展，以360度全方位鏡頭拍攝展覽會場，並於7月21日至8月10日舉行並開放，網友可以以第一身視角「親臨」展覽場地，不過網友仍需要付300日圓（約$21港幣）作為入場費。"},{"pid":"d50a1c85ccc080365bae264fe6a456631ee17a9e","tid":2096660,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T09:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200705/356568384021860352.jpeg/3GGPkfJbkKnXduIDfv9ym7V9QuIJx50EvAHvdLwB73Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200705%2F356568384021860352.jpeg%2F3GGPkfJbkKnXduIDfv9ym7V9QuIJx50EvAHvdLwB73Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=59719baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3554766/org/459dacfcff600b917f0e13cb6aa7811a.jpg/L-j2bbjL_rjf0jNCWb_wO1PIabP_Z8_m2qX3D9ql9w8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3554766%2Forg%2F459dacfcff600b917f0e13cb6aa7811a.jpg%2FL-j2bbjL_rjf0jNCWb_wO1PIabP_Z8_m2qX3D9ql9w8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5187b43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3321180/org/d2e7b0f844d29b4a4e3679739664d296.jpg/98q3AhDXhkavw7C0NMLXugYbLdcOOHH_o_B4IKPw